The '''Blue [[Brubb]]''' was a cantina in [[Mos Espa/Legends|Mos Espa]] on [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]]. It was known to serve the drink, [[Ruby bliel]]. It was located in a part of town controlled by [[Jabba Desilijic Tiure/Legends|Jabba Desilijic Tiure]].

